Nzima died earlier this month in a Mpumalanga hospital, at the age of 83. BUSHBUCKRIDGE - Sam Nzima, the photojournalist best known for taking the picture of a dying Hector Pieterson, is being laid to rest at Lillydale, Bushbuckridge in Mpumalanga. Nzima died earlier this month in a Mpumalanga hospital, at the age of 83. WATCH: Photo journo Sam Nzima laid to rest 